				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Hi. In my emulator, the APU generates 1 sample at each odd CPU cycle. The resampling method I use, in short words, is calculated as the arithmetical average (sum all the samples, divided by the number of samples).<br /><br />Is there another method, not so much complicated?<br />Thank you.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

