					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Problem: the sound output volume is quite low. If I take the result and &lt;&lt; 1, it becomes too high. So, I use a crap decay, volume -= volume &gt;&gt; 1, every time a sample (from resampling) is generated. It works, but it's still cracking depending of the number of active channels.</div>

