					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It would be possible for each sound channel, instead of applying it in the final mixed sample.<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">output = (value * 192) &gt;&gt; 7;<br />output_dac = (duty_sign)? output: -output;</div><br /><strong>value</strong> is the <em>unsigned sample</em> generated in a channel. <strong><em>Usually</em></strong>, it would be:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">output_dac = (duty_sign)? : output: 0;</div></div>

					
							<br /><br />
							<span class="gensmall">Last edited by <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=39">Zepper</a> on Wed Jan 08, 2014 12:23 pm, edited 1 time in total.</span>
